01:55:25.760 --> 01:55:30.560
[Guest]: Yeah, exactly, you know, but you get, you know, it's not as difficult right now to fight

01:55:30.560 --> 01:55:33.920
[Guest]: for a food house because there's far more jobs being introduced into the economy, right,

01:55:33.920 --> 01:55:35.760
