[Guest]: What is the name?

01:55:51.120 --> 01:55:53.760
[Amit Varma]: Shah Rukh Khan films, what is the name?

01:55:53.760 --> 01:55:54.760
[Amit Varma]: Rahul, right?

01:55:54.760 --> 01:55:55.760
[Guest]: Rahul.

01:55:55.760 --> 01:55:56.760
[Guest]: He's Rahul.

01:55:56.760 --> 01:56:00.280
[Guest]: He's Rahul and he's in every film and he's, you know, spreading his arms and he's looking

01:56:00.280 --> 01:56:04.400
[Guest]: for the love of his life and because that's what he needs right now.

01:56:04.400 --> 01:56:09.320
[Guest]: And then Rahul went on for, again, another 10-15 years, K3G, till then, 2000s, later

01:56:09.320 --> 01:56:14.360
[Guest]: late 2000s, Rahul kept going, Raj kept going, Rahul kept going, Shah Rukh Khan's romance

01:56:14.360 --> 01:56:15.440
[Guest]: period.

01:56:15.440 --> 01:56:19.640
[Guest]: After that got over, you had a third kind of a hero, you know, that now that you found

01:56:19.640 --> 01:56:24.120
