01:56:24.120 --> 01:56:29.280
[Guest]: people became more, you know, brave and courageous to talk about love with their families.

01:56:29.280 --> 01:56:31.160
[Guest]: You don't really need to kind of fight for love.

01:56:31.160 --> 01:56:33.560
[Guest]: You didn't need to like, it was an open conversation.

01:56:33.560 --> 01:56:35.000
[Guest]: Shah Rukh Khan normalized it.

01:56:35.000 --> 01:56:39.160
[Guest]: So now when you have all of this, you have Roti, Kapda, Makaan and you have love, what

01:56:39.160 --> 01:56:40.440
[Guest]: do you now need?

01:56:40.440 --> 01:56:44.440
[Guest]: Then the answer came to like, you know, you need to find who you are, you need to now

01:56:44.440 --> 01:56:45.440
[Guest]: go internal.

01:56:45.440 --> 01:56:47.880
[Guest]: Everything was external till now, now it's about to become yours.

01:56:47.880 --> 01:56:52.880
