[Guest]: So, so, okay, as an example, you know, and again, no disrespect to, you know, the, to

01:59:33.840 --> 01:59:38.480
[Guest]: my alma mater, you know, again, one of the best times I've ever had, I must say it, and

01:59:38.480 --> 01:59:41.760
[Guest]: I'm not saying it for any other reason, because I genuinely loved working there.

01:59:41.760 --> 01:59:48.880
[Guest]: Hichki, which was, which Rani Mukherjee ultimately, you know, did, was written for a man.

01:59:48.880 --> 01:59:55.000
[Guest]: It was written and they took it to different men, and different men, like, just weren't,

01:59:55.000 --> 01:59:58.400
[Guest]: you know, like, I don't know if I want to be a teacher or whatever it is.

01:59:58.400 --> 02:00:03.080
[Guest]: And ultimately, then they rethought it and said, what if we attach a bigger actor, but

02:00:03.080 --> 02:00:04.160
[Guest]: it's a female.

02:00:04.160 --> 02:00:08.640
[Guest]: And suddenly the film became monetizable, because when it's a female, you also pay her

02:00:08.640 --> 02:00:12.840
[Guest]: lab because of the gender parity in our country and in all industries.

02:00:12.840 --> 02:00:15.320
[Guest]: So the budget of the film doesn't exceed a certain amount.

02:00:15.320 --> 02:00:17.360
[Guest]: So it's easy to recover the money also.

02:00:17.360 --> 02:00:21.360
[Guest]: So everything then became business wise, it became, you're putting low cost, but low investment.

02:00:21.360 --> 02:00:25.120
[Guest]: And then the return can be in certain cases can be a lot more, right?

02:00:25.120 --> 02:00:30.520
[Guest]: So it's, this is the way that, you know, female women in our country have gotten their own

02:00:30.520 --> 02:00:31.640
[Guest]: films.

02:00:31.640 --> 02:00:34.400
[Guest]: It's only happened after men refused to do those films.

02:00:34.400 --> 02:00:39.040
[Guest]: And women, when you look at any female led film in our country, now, again, I'm using

02:00:39.040 --> 02:00:42.860
[Guest]: that term, because that's the easiest way of identifying them, right?

02:00:42.860 --> 02:00:47.520
[Guest]: If you look at any of these films led by women actors, you will have a film which Shahrukh

02:00:47.520 --> 02:00:51.080
[Guest]: Khan, Salman Khan, anybody, no matter who it is, will lead.

02:00:51.080 --> 02:00:56.360
[Guest]: And you will have any actor between a Deepika to an Anushka, all the big actors of our times

02:00:56.360 --> 02:01:00.880
