02:03:06.320 --> 02:03:08.780
[Guest]: so I was having a conversation with Rajkumar Rao.

02:03:08.780 --> 02:03:15.600
[Guest]: This was, I was interviewing him at a film festival in, in IIT and Queen had just come

02:03:15.600 --> 02:03:18.440
[Guest]: and I said, like, you know, Rajkumar, your work in Queen was just incredible.

02:03:18.440 --> 02:03:21.480
[Guest]: It's so great to see you in like that role where you are going, you know, you're not

02:03:21.480 --> 02:03:24.960
