[Guest]: I mean, we had not spoken for a bit.

03:16:19.280 --> 03:16:23.520
[Guest]: We had become decent friends, but never for a, we just kind of lost touch in the middle.

03:16:23.520 --> 03:16:26.520
[Guest]: We were in different sections and different batches.

03:16:26.520 --> 03:16:29.320
[Guest]: One day again, power cut happened, fourth year, final year of college.

03:16:29.320 --> 03:16:30.320
[Guest]: I've already got two jobs.

03:16:30.320 --> 03:16:34.840
[Guest]: I've got Accenture, CSE, bit of sort in that sense and you know, I'm like, now I'm chilling

03:16:34.840 --> 03:16:40.400
[Guest]: as a senior, nothing to do, two jobs, you can't get more, like to cap at two.

03:16:40.400 --> 03:16:43.280
[Guest]: This guy meets me in a power cut, he's like, how's your life going, kaise chal rahi hai

03:16:43.280 --> 03:16:44.280
[Guest]: zindagi?

03:16:44.280 --> 03:16:46.000
[Guest]: I'm just like, yaar, accha chal raha hai, got two jobs, etc.

03:16:46.000 --> 03:16:50.160
[Guest]: He's like, acha, tu bhi yeh hi karega, tu ne toh bola tha ki, I mean, tere uska kya hua

03:16:50.160 --> 03:16:54.120
[Guest]: writing, writing ga, tu bahut likhta tha us time par bhi, young times, old times, four

03:16:54.120 --> 03:16:55.120
[Guest]: years ago.

03:16:55.120 --> 03:16:57.760
[Guest]: I was like, haan, main soch raha hun ki, and this was my plan at that time, ki main, you

03:16:57.760 --> 03:17:02.240
[Guest]: know, one of the jobs, CSE, will give me Bombay as the, which is the place you want to be

03:17:02.240 --> 03:17:03.240
[Guest]: located.

03:17:03.240 --> 03:17:04.240
[Guest]: They give you the option.

03:17:04.240 --> 03:17:10.480
[Guest]: I will go to Bombay and, you know, main din mein yeh karunga, side mein na main, you know,

03:17:10.480 --> 03:17:11.480
[Guest]: writing karunga, and that's how, like, it's my plan right now.

03:17:11.480 --> 03:17:13.560
[Guest]: Aur jab wo chalne lag jayega, then I will leave it and do this.

03:17:13.560 --> 03:17:18.360
[Guest]: And this guy is just very nonchalantly, in the complete nonchalance, said like, he's

03:17:18.360 --> 03:17:23.520
[Guest]: like, haan, sahi idea hai, tu aisa karna, tu pehle Bombay jaana, side mein yeh karna,

03:17:23.520 --> 03:17:27.640
[Guest]: phir tu MBA karna, side mein writing karna, phir shadi karna, side mein writing karna,

03:17:27.640 --> 03:17:30.840
[Guest]: phir bache karna, side mein writing karna, phir tu ek din mar jayega na, tu writing

03:17:30.840 --> 03:17:31.840
[Guest]: side mein rehgi.

03:17:31.840 --> 03:17:38.320
[Guest]: You know, aur bolte bolte bol gaya, and you know, chal bhai, what, I mean, you do just

03:17:38.320 --> 03:17:44.960
[Guest]: like, I, suddenly my life flashed in my entire, in front of my eyes, and I was like, that

03:17:44.960 --> 03:17:45.960
[Guest]: is so true.

03:17:45.960 --> 03:17:50.560
[Guest]: I could just be doing this, and that's what I'd been doing till then, since 14 to now,

03:17:50.560 --> 03:17:55.200
[Guest]: I was 20 at that time, 6 years, all of this were, these were side pursuits for me.

03:17:55.200 --> 03:17:59.840
[Guest]: They were never the, because, again, arts nahi kar sakte hai, toh hobby hai, this cannot

03:17:59.840 --> 03:18:01.120
[Guest]: be your live stream.

03:18:01.120 --> 03:18:06.680
[Guest]: And then I realized, like, I have, I now already had two jobs, and one of them was in, you

03:18:06.680 --> 03:18:10.520
[Guest]: know, July, I had to join in July, and one I have to join in August.

03:18:10.520 --> 03:18:12.600
[Guest]: My college finished in April.

03:18:12.600 --> 03:18:16.720
[Guest]: So then I was like, from the time this conversation happened, which I think would have been in

03:18:16.720 --> 03:18:22.080
[Guest]: the end of first semester, beginning of second semester, I said, I have now 6 to 8 months.

03:18:22.080 --> 03:18:23.480
[Guest]: He's absolutely right.

03:18:23.480 --> 03:18:24.480
[Guest]: Let me give it a shot.

03:18:24.480 --> 03:18:25.480
[Guest]: Let me try.

03:18:25.480 --> 03:18:26.960
[Guest]: Why am I saying that ki side mein karenge?

03:18:26.960 --> 03:18:28.240
[Guest]: If I get a job, I will go for it.

03:18:28.240 --> 03:18:29.240
[Guest]: If I get a good job.

03:18:29.240 --> 03:18:32.000
[Guest]: I already have like a safety net now.

03:18:32.000 --> 03:18:33.000
[Guest]: I need to give it a shot.

03:18:33.000 --> 03:18:35.200
[Guest]: I did everything possible.

