[Guest]: CSC is a big company, right?

03:24:16.120 --> 03:24:19.840
[Guest]: Like, you know, when for computer and computer students, it's a big deal.

03:24:19.840 --> 03:24:25.360
[Guest]: And I got it very easily, like, in you know, how are these first whatever I was technically

