[Guest]: proficient enough to clear technical, I was not like the best student, I was like seven

03:24:29.920 --> 03:24:35.480
[Guest]: point something I'd gotten a seven pointer, but but it was technically decent enough and

03:24:35.480 --> 03:24:38.560
[Guest]: smart enough to crack their test or whatever it is.

