05:16:08.040 --> 05:16:10.040
[Guest]: And one of the other kids from Maharashtra

05:16:10.040 --> 05:16:12.040
[Guest]: Had passed away, because he drowned

05:16:12.040 --> 05:16:14.040
[Guest]: In, I think that's what it was, he drowned

05:16:14.040 --> 05:16:16.040
[Guest]: In a river nearby

05:16:16.040 --> 05:16:18.040
[Guest]: And he's like, none of us

05:16:18.040 --> 05:16:20.040
[Guest]: Just knew how to process this

05:16:20.040 --> 05:16:22.040
[Guest]: We were all kids from Maharashtra

05:16:22.040 --> 05:16:24.040
[Guest]: We used to have our own group

