[Guest]: And then just we stopped talking

05:16:26.040 --> 05:16:28.040
[Guest]: Because we were just sad

05:16:28.040 --> 05:16:30.040
[Guest]: And we didn't know how to process

05:16:30.040 --> 05:16:32.040
[Guest]: He's like, and then I remembered what happened

05:16:32.040 --> 05:16:34.040
[Guest]: In the day that we did that storytelling

05:16:34.040 --> 05:16:36.040
[Guest]: Thing in IIIT

05:16:36.040 --> 05:16:38.040
[Guest]: And he's like, I realized that maybe we need to

05:16:38.040 --> 05:16:40.040
[Guest]: Create a safe space, so he said

05:16:40.040 --> 05:16:42.040
[Guest]: That I created this

05:16:42.040 --> 05:16:44.040
[Guest]: Club name called

05:16:44.040 --> 05:16:46.040
[Guest]: Marathi Mitra Mandir

05:16:46.040 --> 05:16:48.040
[Guest]: And he's like, I would just tell everybody

05:16:48.040 --> 05:16:50.040
[Guest]: That we are part of the Marathi Mitra Mandir

05:16:50.040 --> 05:16:52.040
[Guest]: And we'll meet every night

05:16:52.040 --> 05:16:54.040
[Guest]: Just to share with us

05:16:54.040 --> 05:16:56.040
[Guest]: Just like we've done on the Rewa Rosh

05:16:56.040 --> 05:16:58.040
[Guest]: And he's like, when I did it in that way

05:16:58.040 --> 05:17:00.040
[Guest]: Suddenly every night

05:17:00.040 --> 05:17:02.040
[Guest]: All these kids who are telling them, let's talk

05:17:02.040 --> 05:17:04.040
[Guest]: And let's talk about how we're going through an express

05:17:04.040 --> 05:17:06.040
[Guest]: Would never do it

05:17:06.040 --> 05:17:08.040
[Guest]: All of these boys came and

05:17:08.040 --> 05:17:10.040
[Guest]: Started expressing and started

05:17:10.040 --> 05:17:12.040
[Guest]: Crying and started speaking

05:17:12.040 --> 05:17:14.040
[Guest]: Like about what happened

05:17:14.040 --> 05:17:16.040
[Guest]: And he's like, we were all able to process because of that

05:17:16.040 --> 05:17:18.040
[Guest]: One little thing that happened

05:17:18.040 --> 05:17:20.040
[Guest]: And there are

05:17:20.040 --> 05:17:22.040
[Guest]: So many more stories like this

05:17:22.040 --> 05:17:24.040
[Guest]: So so so many stories like this that

05:17:24.040 --> 05:17:26.040
[Guest]: I've heard across this and it's not just the stories

05:17:26.040 --> 05:17:28.040
[Guest]: Of what has happened on the road show

05:17:28.040 --> 05:17:30.040
[Guest]: But the stories of what has happened beyond

05:17:30.040 --> 05:17:32.040
[Guest]: And the stories of like when I would go

05:17:32.040 --> 05:17:34.040
[Guest]: Back or when I would hear from these kids again

05:17:34.040 --> 05:17:36.040
[Guest]: About all the wonderful

05:17:36.040 --> 05:17:38.040
[Guest]: Wonderful things in the way in which they have

05:17:38.040 --> 05:17:40.040
[Guest]: Used these safe spaces

05:17:40.040 --> 05:17:42.040
[Guest]: In the way that they become more empathetic

05:17:42.040 --> 05:17:44.040
[Guest]: In the way that they have created

05:17:44.040 --> 05:17:46.040
[Guest]: Safe spaces for others who have

05:17:46.040 --> 05:17:48.040
[Guest]: Passed it on, you know, if

05:17:48.040 --> 05:17:50.040
[Guest]: Anger begets anger, kindness begets

05:17:50.040 --> 05:17:52.040
[Guest]: Kindness, if

05:17:52.040 --> 05:17:54.040
[Guest]: Toxicity can grow, so can kindness

05:17:54.040 --> 05:17:56.040
[Guest]: You just need to

05:17:56.040 --> 05:17:58.040
[Guest]: You know, start that

05:17:58.040 --> 05:18:00.040
[Guest]: Start by listening, you start by

05:18:00.040 --> 05:18:02.040
[Guest]: Sharing, you start by

05:18:02.040 --> 05:18:04.040
[Guest]: Creating a safe space for someone else

05:18:04.040 --> 05:18:06.040
[Guest]: And someone will do the same for you

05:18:06.040 --> 05:18:08.040
[Guest]: I can promise that because that's really

05:18:08.040 --> 05:18:10.040
[Guest]: What I've seen, not just from the road show but from

05:18:10.040 --> 05:18:12.040
[Guest]: Everywhere else, the amount of

05:18:12.040 --> 05:18:14.040
[Guest]: You know, when the, when I spoke about

05:18:14.040 --> 05:18:16.040
[Guest]: My story of anxiety, you know, online

05:18:18.040 --> 05:18:20.040
[Guest]: I could not have, it was

05:18:20.040 --> 05:18:22.040
[Guest]: I was so nervous, I remember like I never

05:18:22.040 --> 05:18:24.040
[Guest]: And I got strength from my students because my students

05:18:24.040 --> 05:18:26.040
[Guest]: Said, would always talk about their stories

05:18:26.040 --> 05:18:28.040
[Guest]: I was like, man, maybe I should also share mine

05:18:28.040 --> 05:18:30.040
[Guest]: Because I've been going through

05:18:30.040 --> 05:18:32.040
[Guest]: Anxiety for the last

05:18:32.040 --> 05:18:34.040
[Guest]: 10-11 months at that time

05:18:34.040 --> 05:18:36.040
[Guest]: And all my social media posts show me

05:18:36.040 --> 05:18:38.040
[Guest]: As like this, like I'm happy, I'm

05:18:38.040 --> 05:18:40.040
[Guest]: Enjoying, my life is great

05:18:40.040 --> 05:18:42.040
[Guest]: How can I not

05:18:42.040 --> 05:18:44.040
[Guest]: I think I owe it to my students

05:18:44.040 --> 05:18:46.040
[Guest]: To talk about my truth as well

05:18:46.040 --> 05:18:48.040
[Guest]: So I wrote this long post

05:18:48.040 --> 05:18:50.040
[Guest]: Closed my eyes, published it, put it

05:18:50.040 --> 05:18:52.040
[Guest]: On Twitter

05:18:52.040 --> 05:18:54.040
[Guest]: And then I came back, I think after 2-3 hours

05:18:54.040 --> 05:18:56.040
[Guest]: And the responses

05:18:56.040 --> 05:18:58.040
[Guest]: Were just

05:18:58.040 --> 05:19:00.040
[Guest]: The

05:19:00.040 --> 05:19:02.040
[Guest]: Compassion

05:19:02.040 --> 05:19:04.040
[Guest]: The love, the kindness

05:19:04.040 --> 05:19:06.040
[Guest]: That I received from all kinds of people

05:19:08.040 --> 05:19:10.040
[Guest]: Who I knew, who I didn't know

05:19:10.040 --> 05:19:12.040
[Guest]: On the internet, the DMs

05:19:12.040 --> 05:19:14.040
[Guest]: Just non-stop like

05:19:14.040 --> 05:19:16.040
[Guest]: Thank you for sharing, you know

05:19:16.040 --> 05:19:18.040
[Guest]: I wish I could, one of my closest friends

05:19:18.040 --> 05:19:20.040
[Guest]: You know the funniest thing that happened

05:19:20.040 --> 05:19:22.040
[Guest]: One of my closest friends who

05:19:22.040 --> 05:19:24.040
[Guest]: I used to meet everyday during

05:19:24.040 --> 05:19:26.040
[Guest]: Every week, we were working together on something at Yashar

05:19:26.040 --> 05:19:28.040
[Guest]: Who has now become one of my

05:19:28.040 --> 05:19:30.040
[Guest]: Dearest, dearest friends, every week we would

05:19:30.040 --> 05:19:32.040
[Guest]: Meet, 2 boys

05:19:32.040 --> 05:19:34.040
[Guest]: 2 men, same age, same kind

05:19:34.040 --> 05:19:36.040
[Guest]: Of like both, you know

05:19:36.040 --> 05:19:38.040
[Guest]: Almost like very similar to each other in many different

05:19:38.040 --> 05:19:40.040
[Guest]: Ways, and after I put this

05:19:40.040 --> 05:19:42.040
[Guest]: Thing, he just came to me, he called me

05:19:42.040 --> 05:19:44.040
[Guest]: And he's like, I didn't know you had anxiety

05:19:44.040 --> 05:19:46.040
[Guest]: I said, why?

05:19:46.040 --> 05:19:48.040
[Guest]: He's like, I also have anxiety, I'm like what?

05:19:48.040 --> 05:19:50.040
[Guest]: He's like, yeah you've been going to a therapist

05:19:50.040 --> 05:19:52.040
[Guest]: I've also been going to a therapist, he's like

05:19:52.040 --> 05:19:54.040
[Guest]: I didn't know that I could share with you

05:19:54.040 --> 05:19:56.040
[Guest]: I was like, can you imagine, we've been

05:19:56.040 --> 05:19:58.040
[Guest]: Like meeting every week for

05:19:58.040 --> 05:20:00.040
[Guest]: 8 months, as 2 men

05:20:00.040 --> 05:20:02.040
[Guest]: Who've become friends with each other

05:20:02.040 --> 05:20:04.040
[Guest]: And we've not been able to say to each other

05:20:04.040 --> 05:20:06.040
[Guest]: That we have anxiety, because that's

05:20:06.040 --> 05:20:08.040
[Guest]: The kind of stigma, but when you share

05:20:08.040 --> 05:20:10.040
[Guest]: The kind of love and empathy that happens

05:20:10.040 --> 05:20:12.040
[Guest]: After that, and now I've become

05:20:12.040 --> 05:20:14.040
[Guest]: That person and we've become these people like

05:20:14.040 --> 05:20:16.040
[Guest]: He just like, every, randomly

05:20:16.040 --> 05:20:18.040
[Guest]: Once in a while, I get a I love you

05:20:18.040 --> 05:20:20.040
[Guest]: From him, that's it, nothing else

05:20:20.040 --> 05:20:22.040
[Guest]: No context, I love you

05:20:22.040 --> 05:20:24.040
[Guest]: I love you, that's it

05:20:24.040 --> 05:20:26.040
[Guest]: And why can't men do that?

05:20:26.040 --> 05:20:28.040
[Guest]: I just find it like, you know, one of the things

05:20:28.040 --> 05:20:30.040
[Guest]: On the internet, that just kind of pet peeves

05:20:30.040 --> 05:20:32.040
[Guest]: Of mine is like, always see, look at

05:20:32.040 --> 05:20:34.040
[Guest]: The way girls champion each other on

05:20:34.040 --> 05:20:36.040
[Guest]: Instagram comments, you put

05:20:36.040 --> 05:20:38.040
[Guest]: Anything, you can put a picture of a sandwich

05:20:38.040 --> 05:20:40.040
[Guest]: And you know the other girls would be like

05:20:40.040 --> 05:20:42.040
[Amit Varma]: Yas queen, eat this sandwich, go for it

05:20:42.040 --> 05:20:44.040
[Guest]: What a beautiful, beautiful thing

05:20:44.040 --> 05:20:46.040
[Guest]: Blah blah blah, guys can do

05:20:46.040 --> 05:20:48.040
[Guest]: Anything, I mean they can have

05:20:48.040 --> 05:20:50.040
[Guest]: Beautiful pictures, they can have

05:20:50.040 --> 05:20:52.040
[Guest]: Like, they can literally change the world and there

05:20:52.040 --> 05:20:54.040
[Guest]: Is still some other guy, one of his best friends in the comments

05:20:54.040 --> 05:20:56.040
[Guest]: Saying, idiot, you know

05:20:56.040 --> 05:20:58.040
[Guest]: What do you think of yourself, what kind of

05:20:58.040 --> 05:21:00.040
[Guest]: Asshole you are, you know, that's the

05:21:00.040 --> 05:21:02.040
[Guest]: So to speak love language

05:21:02.040 --> 05:21:04.040
[Guest]: You are not

05:21:04.040 --> 05:21:06.040
[Guest]: So few people, even right now

05:21:06.040 --> 05:21:08.040
[Guest]: As somebody who really talks a lot about

05:21:08.040 --> 05:21:10.040
[Guest]: Again, mental health, empathy, etc

05:21:10.040 --> 05:21:12.040
[Guest]: 70% of my

05:21:12.040 --> 05:21:14.040
[Guest]: Followers at this point are

05:21:14.040 --> 05:21:16.040
[Guest]: Women, 80-90%

05:21:16.040 --> 05:21:18.040
[Guest]: Of my comments are women

05:21:18.040 --> 05:21:20.040
[Guest]: And I might be talking about

05:21:20.040 --> 05:21:22.040
[Guest]: Masculinity, let me tell you that, I might

05:21:22.040 --> 05:21:24.040
[Guest]: Write a post about masculinity and there is like

05:21:24.040 --> 05:21:26.040
[Guest]: 90% women talking about it, you know

05:21:26.040 --> 05:21:28.040
[Guest]: Thank you for saying this, etc, where are the men?

05:21:28.040 --> 05:21:30.040
[Guest]: Why are you so afraid of talking, it's not like they are not

05:21:30.040 --> 05:21:32.040
[Guest]: Seen, I know that they are

05:21:32.040 --> 05:21:34.040
[Guest]: Seen, I know that, you know

05:21:34.040 --> 05:21:36.040
[Guest]: Because they comment on some other random

05:21:36.040 --> 05:21:38.040
[Guest]: Things I might do, but a few of them

05:21:38.040 --> 05:21:40.040
[Guest]: Who are comfortable with their masculinity

05:21:40.040 --> 05:21:42.040
[Guest]: Would probably even now send

05:21:42.040 --> 05:21:44.040
[Guest]: Hearts or whatever, but they would fit into

05:21:44.040 --> 05:21:46.040
[Guest]: Because he is a poet, that's why he is doing it

05:21:46.040 --> 05:21:48.040
[Guest]: There is a writer who might be doing this

05:21:48.040 --> 05:21:50.040
[Guest]: You know, but otherwise traditionally

05:21:50.040 --> 05:21:52.040
[Guest]: You just don't do it, but why?

05:21:52.040 --> 05:21:54.040
[Guest]: It's okay

05:21:54.040 --> 05:21:56.040
[Guest]: Go online and share love

05:21:56.040 --> 05:21:58.040
[Guest]: Put hearts, you know, let people

05:21:58.040 --> 05:22:00.040
[Guest]: Know that you love them

05:22:00.040 --> 05:22:02.040
[Guest]: Let boys know you love them

05:22:02.040 --> 05:22:04.040
[Guest]: Give them hugs, it's okay

05:22:04.040 --> 05:22:06.040
[Guest]: The world will become far more

05:22:06.040 --> 05:22:08.040
[Guest]: Non-toxic if we are able to put our

05:22:08.040 --> 05:22:10.040
[Guest]: Stories out there and we are able to

05:22:10.040 --> 05:22:12.040
[Guest]: Share it with people

05:22:12.040 --> 05:22:14.040
[Guest]: Because that's what stories do, they just bring

05:22:14.040 --> 05:22:16.040
[Guest]: This kind of incredible wave of empathy

05:22:16.040 --> 05:22:18.040
[Guest]: And love that all of us

05:22:18.040 --> 05:22:20.040
[Guest]: Need in our lives, but we need to

05:22:20.040 --> 05:22:22.040
[Guest]: Need to have that courage and one last point

05:22:22.040 --> 05:22:24.040
[Guest]: Right now, which is that

05:22:24.040 --> 05:22:26.040
[Guest]: This is also the power of the internet, right

05:22:26.040 --> 05:22:28.040
[Guest]: Where you have, where it can be used

05:22:28.040 --> 05:22:30.040
[Guest]: In all these terrible and negative ways

05:22:30.040 --> 05:22:32.040
[Guest]: You can also

05:22:32.040 --> 05:22:34.040
[Guest]: The incredible power of it is

05:22:34.040 --> 05:22:36.040
[Guest]: That you can also use it in incredibly

05:22:36.040 --> 05:22:38.040
[Guest]: Positive ways, you can

05:22:38.040 --> 05:22:40.040
[Guest]: Use this, if you don't have a community

