[Guest]: Has happened so often with me and I've seen

05:23:02.040 --> 05:23:04.040
[Guest]: It happen so often with others, I just

05:23:04.040 --> 05:23:06.040
[Guest]: Use it to the incredible

05:23:06.040 --> 05:23:08.040
[Guest]: Potential it has, you know, put

05:23:08.040 --> 05:23:10.040
[Guest]: Your story out there and you'll see that

05:23:10.040 --> 05:23:12.040
[Guest]: You know, more often than not, there are people who are

05:23:12.040 --> 05:23:14.040
[Guest]: Who will cheer for you

