[Amit Varma]: This has been a pet peeve of mine and something that I've

05:23:30.040 --> 05:23:32.040
[Amit Varma]: Realized that I've been guilty of as well

05:23:32.040 --> 05:23:34.040
[Amit Varma]: That men just don't express

05:23:34.040 --> 05:23:36.040
[Amit Varma]: The way they feel, especially to other men

05:23:36.040 --> 05:23:38.040
[Amit Varma]: I did an episode a while back with

05:23:38.040 --> 05:23:40.040
[Amit Varma]: A few months back with an old friend of mine

05:23:40.040 --> 05:23:42.040
[Amit Varma]: Chandra Raj Choudhary

05:23:42.040 --> 05:23:44.040
[Amit Varma]: And like

