[Amit Varma]: Your own issues, at a point

05:24:20.040 --> 05:24:22.040
[Amit Varma]: In time where you are

05:24:22.040 --> 05:24:24.040
[Amit Varma]: Incredibly successful, right

05:24:24.040 --> 05:24:26.040
[Amit Varma]: You are at Yash Raj, you've made

